text: Ammara Butt is a Pakistani television actress. She is known for her role as Komal in Ranjha Ranjha Kardi (2018). She made her debut as a lead actress in A-Plus TV's Hoor Pari (2019). Her other appearances include Meherbaan (2017), De Ijazat (2018), Aakhri Station (2018) and Ajnabi Lage Zindagi (2019). ==Television== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Year!!Title!!Role !Network!!
